'''君士坦丁堡條約'''<ref>{{cite book |title=''Slavonic Europe - A Political History of Poland from 1447 to 1796'' |last=Bain |first=R. Nisbet |year=2006年 |publisher=READ BOOKS |isbn=1-84664-581-6 |pages=第323页 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PdZBZcUbSewC&pg=PA323&dq=%2B1724+%2B%22treaty+of+constantinople%22&as_brr=3&sig=GaIILut0CK9aTLKgiWYZHX8Fl8g |access-date=2015-05-24 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811211512/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PdZBZcUbSewC&pg=PA323&dq=%2B1724+%2B%22treaty+of+constantinople%22&as_brr=3&sig=GaIILut0CK9aTLKgiWYZHX8Fl8g |dead-url=no }}</ref>或称作'''俄奥条约'''<ref>{{cite book |title=''Iran Under the Safavids'' |last=Savory |first=Roger |year=1980年 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=0-521-04251-8 |pages=第252页 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=v4Yr4foWFFgC&pg=PA252&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=_beplI2bS1KPNEWnk1nvQRMZxPQ |access-date=2015-08-13 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105173017/https://books.google.com/books?id=v4Yr4foWFFgC&pg=PA252&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=_beplI2bS1KPNEWnk1nvQRMZxPQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、'''瓜分波斯条约'''(''Iran Mukasemenamesi'')<ref name="martin">{{cite book |title=''Uralic And Altaic Series'' |last=Martin |first=Samuel Elmo |year=1997 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=0-7007-0380-2 |pages=第47页 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UWYdLuA34OQC&pg=PA49&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=RCQz1SyXQfwl3QxvSpHrsomBKqI#PPA47,M1 |access-date=2015-08-13 |archive-date=2016-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160615093435/https://books.google.com/books?id=UWYdLuA34OQC&pg=PA49&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=RCQz1SyXQfwl3QxvSpHrsomBKqI#PPA47,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是1724年[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]]與[[奧斯曼帝國|奧斯曼帝國]]為[[波斯|波斯]][[萨菲王朝|萨菲王朝]]問題簽署的條約。

當俄羅斯帝國與奧斯曼帝國雙方為佔據更多的波斯領土而即將戰爭時，[[法國|法國]]作為中介進行干預<ref>{{cite book |title=''The Cambridge History of Iran'' |last=Fisher |first=William Bayne |year=1968年 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=0-521-20095-4 |pages=第320页 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=H20Xt157iYUC&pg=PA322&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=30fbi1zn1zb5ifv_BF2JBguzFUg#PPA320,M1 |access-date=2015-05-24 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095544/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=H20Xt157iYUC&pg=PA322&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=30fbi1zn1zb5ifv_BF2JBguzFUg#PPA320,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在1722至1723年的俄罗斯帝国与波斯战争中，俄罗斯帝国征服了波斯萨菲王朝北部的大片土地，北高加索、外高加索地区和萨菲王朝本土的北部领土被纳入俄罗斯帝国统治<ref>Alexander Mikaberidze. [https://books.google.nl/books?id=jBBYD2J2oE4C&pg=PA1024&lpg=PA1024&dq=russo-Persian+War+1722-1723&source=bl&ots=MG6HP72DpJ&sig=I8Akh1ZL_tO-CpsYWIn6CrgVTFo&hl=nl&sa=X&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAzgKahUKEwi6hrmWvubGAhXCNxQKHVDNAt8#v=onepage&q=russo-Persian%20War%201722-1723&f=false "Conflict and Conquest in the Islamic World: A Historical Encyclopedia: A Historical Encyclopedia"] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.nl/books?id=jBBYD2J2oE4C&pg=PA1024&lpg=PA1024&dq=russo-Persian+War+1722-1723&source=bl&ots=MG6HP72DpJ&sig=I8Akh1ZL_tO-CpsYWIn6CrgVTFo&hl=nl&sa=X&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAzgKahUKEwi6hrmWvubGAhXCNxQKHVDNAt8#v=onepage&q=russo-Persian%20War%201722-1723&f=false |date=20201206044809 }} ABC-CLIO 2011. 第 726页</ref>，而奥斯曼土耳其帝国已侵略并占领了萨菲王朝西部的所有领土、尤其是格鲁吉亚和亚美尼亚的大部分土地。兩國政府於簽署的條約在君士坦丁堡1724年6月12日簽署條約<ref>{{cite book |title=''E. J. Brill's First Encyclopaedia of Islam, 1913-1936'' |last=Houtsma |first=M. Th. |coauthors=van Donzel, E. |year=1993年 |publisher=BRILL |isbn=90-04-08265-4 |pages=第760页 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ro--tXw_hxMC&pg=PA760&dq=%2B1724+%2Btreaty+%2Bottoman+%2Brussia&as_brr=3&sig=orLtpRFya8SvSAgXc8p3NsxFhqM |access-date=2015-05-24 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407091751/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ro--tXw_hxMC&pg=PA760&dq=+1724++treaty++ottoman++russia&as_brr=3&sig=orLtpRFya8SvSAgXc8p3NsxFhqM |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。把[[高加索|高加索]]地區[[庫爾河|庫爾河]]與[[阿拉斯河|阿拉斯河]]以東地方給予俄羅斯（今伊朗的[[吉兰省|吉兰省]]、[[马赞德兰省|马赞德兰省]]、[[戈尔甘|阿斯塔拉般德]]以及[[达吉斯坦共和国|达吉斯坦]]）以西歸奧斯曼帝國<ref name="martin"/>。

